1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>공부할것</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>서버로부터 비동기 데이터를 프론트에서 잘 받아 활용하는 방법\n<ul>\n<li>web rtc 혹은 web socket 과 같은 기술들을 살펴볼 것, 더 가벼운 방법은 없는지도…</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>PWA를 활용한 알림메시지 전달방식 공부하기</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"개발-아이디어\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C-%EC%95%84%EC%9D%B4%EB%94%94%EC%96%B4\" aria-label=\"개발 아이디어 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개발 아이디어</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Flutter로 간단한 토이프로젝트를 해볼까나?</li>\n<li>자주 사용하는 Es lint config 만들기\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://tech.kakao.com/2019/12/05/make-better-use-of-eslint/\">참고링크</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"-일상관련\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%9D%BC%EC%83%81%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8\" aria-label=\" 일상관련 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.9